import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter, SimpleGrid, Text, Heading, Grid } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function Result( {results} ) {
    const frontalResults = results['Frontal Results'];
    return (
        <Grid mt={15} templateColumns='repeat(3, 1fr)' gap={8}>
            <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                    <Heading size='md'>Diagnosis Result</Heading>
                </CardHeader>
            <CardBody textAlign={'left'}>
                <Text>Tipe Wajah: {frontalResults['Tipe Wajah']}</Text>
                <Text>Simetris Wajah:</Text>
                <Text>Keseimbangan Transversal:</Text>
                <Text>Keseimbangan Vertikal:</Text>
            </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
            <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                    <Heading size='md'>Diagnosis Result</Heading>
                </CardHeader>
            <CardBody textAlign={'left'}>
                <Text>Garis Midline Wajah:</Text>
                <Text>Bukal Koridor:</Text>
                <Text>Kurva Senyum:</Text>
                <Text>Garis Senyum:</Text>
            </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
            <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                    <Heading size='md'>Diagnosis Result</Heading>
                </CardHeader>
            <CardBody textAlign={'left'}>
                <Text>Profil Wajah:</Text>
                <Text>Sudut Mentolabial:</Text>
                <Text>Sudut Nasolabial:</Text>
            </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
        </Grid>
    );
}


export default Result;
